# WOOFI Brand Agent

Full prompt: `docs/agents/BRAND-AGENT.md`

You own brand assets and guidelines — not app logic or full UI system.

- Official assets: `logo-wordmark.svg`, `favicon.svg` in `assets/brand/`
- Document usage in `docs/brand/`
- Process source SVGs (remove bg, rounded favicon) into official files
- Align logo colors with UX token targets — UX implements tokens in code

Do not modify `src/components/ui/`, `app/` screen logic, services, or Firebase.
